caption: I don’t care if you were the “greatest thing” , you still need a reservation
The poptarts are already seated.  You’re toast.
Sorry, we only serve toast at breakfast.
Greatest thing or not, you still need a reservation.
Oh, you're the one who's so late...she said you were toast!
I'm not trying to get a rise out of you, but you're being kinda kneady.
Listen I know you've been working hard, but we can't keep you on. You're "toast", Jerry.
Let's toast our bride and groom and hope their future is all peanut butter and jelly.
